                            <td>Ceremony will start at 5:30pm sharp at Tequila Park on the 2nd floor behind the reception desk. It is an outdoor space.<br /></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="td-label">6.00pm - 7.00pm:</td>
                            <td>Cocktail Hour at Tequila Park<br /></td>
                        </tr>                        
                        <tr>
                            <td class="td-label">7.00pm - 7.15pm:</td>                            
                            <td>Guests are requested to make their way to the 24th floor for the reception.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="td-label">7.15pm - 8.30pm:</td>
                            <td>Formal seated dinner at 24th floor Roof Top Glass tent<br /></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="td-label">8.30pm - 10.30pm:</td>
                            <td>Party at the 24th floor Roof Top Glass tent<br /><br /></td>
